---
title: Carb Smart Middle Eastern-Style Beyond Meat® Bowls with Creamy Hummus Dressing
description: Skip the pita and layer this plate with all your favourite shawarma toppings. We love this Beyond Meat® dish with roasted carrots, sweet tomatoes, pickled onions, olives and a creamy hummus dressing.

